xpswitch:
~~~~~~~~~
Switch your xp version by linking an xp.ini symlink to a
cetail version configuration.
 - xp-<version>.ini needs to be in the ~/.xp directory
 - an xp-current.ini should be available for the xp head checkout

Usage: xpswitch [<version>]
 - version defaults to "current"

Example: $> xpswitch 5.7.5


xpinstall:
~~~~~~~~~~
Install a new xp version. an xp-<version>.ini will be written to
the ~/.xp directory.
 - xp libraries should be located in ~/xp
 - xp.ini files should be located in ~/.xp

Usage: xpinstall <version>

Example: $> xpinstall 5.7.5

